### Key design decisions:
- Input validation runs **before** resource existence checks (tests expect 422 for bad input even on non-existent waitlists)
- Body size limit set to 64,000 bytes (test payload is ~65KB)
- `open_db()` sets a module-level DB reference; `get_db()` retrieves it lazily for route handlers
- Atomic score updates via `UPDATE SET score = score + ?` (no read-modify-write race)
- SSRF validation rejects private IPs, link-local, localhost, and metadata endpoints

